	"https://github.com/Loyalsoldier/v2ray-rules-dat/releases/download/${pkgver}/geosite.dat")
sha256sums=('4411ae669b5c44f51f07eac28fc7c8ba7f6bf72aa058663bbe5ce4b065c52cc9'
            'db288cafe77bdd12a930ab26a05531c1bd1ceaa1c3aa35772fdd3505b9bc6785')

